author: Laurence Norman
title: Britain’s Transition Phase Out of EU Will Likely Look Like Status Quo
text:
It’s time to talk transition. In coming weeks, Brexit negotiations will turn to what happens in the period immediately after Britain’s departure from the European Union on March 29, 2019.
We know more or less what the transition will look like. It will replicate EU membership with one big difference: Britain will lose its say in EU decision-making.
